node.text:
Try this 🔥 Full Body Workout ‪⚡️ :30 seconds each exercise, 5 rounds. :60 rest between rounds. 💥

1. Diver push-ups
2. Tricep pushups
3. Jump tucks
4. Ski lunges (right & left leg) 
5. Slider planks to pike 
6. Windshield wipers
7. Candlestick 💥 

— Tag a friend you’d do this full body workout with 💥 

🎼 WizKid ft. Drake - Come Closer

node.text:
💥 SIX (6) rounds :20 seconds work, :10 seconds rest  NO rest in between rounds 💥

•

1. Jump Rope 
2. Straight Punches 
3. Uppercuts 
4.  Push-Ups (AMRAP) 
5. Squats (AMRAP) 
6. Side Plank Leg Raises (AMRAP) 

•

💥 Tag your workout friends you would do this HIIT program with and save for later 💥
